history.content: That's a great question for your ESS advisor.

I am an EECS sophomore and am satisfactorily meeting my graduation requirements in terms of units (only need around 6 classes left to meet my graduation requirements). This semester I was looking into a scenario where I can take a lighter courseload. If I take Stat20, ENGIN 7, and Film R1B, does Stat20 and ENGIN 7 count as non-required technical classes? Thank you.
